<section class="project-map" aria-label="X51C AI 商品图项目运行地图">
  <header class="map-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">HOW THE PROJECT RUNS</span>
      <h2>运营只进一个入口，后面由 Skill 分工完成</h2>
      <p>这张图既是使用流程，也是项目架构。第一次使用时顺着箭头走；以后排查问题，也顺着同一条链往回找。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-summary" aria-label="项目结构概览">
      <span><b>1</b> 个总入口</span>
      <span><b>2</b> 个专业 Skill</span>
      <span><b>2</b> 份状态文件</span>
      <span><b>1</b> 个图片生成层</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="usage-strip" aria-label="运营使用流程">
    <div class="usage-step">
      <span>01</span>
      <strong>准备资料</strong>
      <small>商品属性、实拍图、竞品链接，可选评价数据</small>
    </div>
    <i>→</i>
    <div class="usage-step">
      <span>02</span>
      <strong>发起任务</strong>
      <small>“我要给 X51C 做一套主图和详情图”</small>
    </div>
    <i>→</i>
    <div class="usage-step">
      <span>03</span>
      <strong>确认方案</strong>
      <small>看整套图片计划，确认卖点、顺序和边界</small>
    </div>
    <i>→</i>
    <div class="usage-step">
      <span>04</span>
      <strong>逐张出图</strong>
      <small>单图生成、审核，有问题就回到对应层修改</small>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="architecture-panel">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <span class="eyebrow">PROJECT ARCHITECTURE</span>
      <h3>一条任务进入项目后，背后到底发生了什么</h3>
      <p>运营不需要手动调用 Skill。总入口负责判断什么时候找谁、什么时候停、什么时候继续。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="architecture-flow">
      <div class="user-node">
        <span class="node-type">USER</span>
        <strong>运营 / 商品负责人</strong>
        <p>输入商品资料、真实照片、竞品链接和可选评价数据。</p>
        <div class="user-prompt">“我要给 X51C 做一套商品图”</div>
      </div>

      <span class="flow-arrow">↓</span>

      <div class="controller-node">
        <div class="controller-head">
          <div>
            <span class="node-type">MAIN SKILL</span>
            <strong>ecommerce-product-image</strong>
            <small>商品图总入口 / 项目负责人</small>
          </div>
          <span class="controller-badge">唯一入口</span>
        </div>
        <div class="controller-actions">
          <span>接收任务</span>
          <span>检查资料</span>
          <span>调用专业 Skill</span>
          <span>汇总判断</span>
          <span>控制流程继续或暂停</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="specialist-branch" aria-label="专业 Skill 分工">
        <div class="branch-line"></div>
        <article class="specialist-card market-card">
          <span class="node-type">SPECIALIST SKILL</span>
          <strong>competitor-analysis</strong>
          <h4>看市场怎么卖</h4>
          <p>打开竞品页面，看首图钩子、主图分工、详情页顺序和视觉机会点。</p>
          <div class="return-note">分析结果返回总入口</div>
        </article>

        <article class="specialist-card review-card">
          <span class="node-type">OPTIONAL SKILL</span>
          <strong>review-analysis</strong>
          <h4>看用户在意什么</h4>
          <p>从评价里找高频关注、误解和痛点；没有评价资料时直接跳过。</p>
          <div class="return-note">分析结果返回总入口</div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <span class="flow-arrow">↓</span>

      <div class="fact-gate">
        <div class="gate-title">
          <span class="node-type">MATERIAL GATE</span>
          <strong>资料和实拍图够不够？</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="gate-cases">
          <div class="gate-case pass">
            <span>够</span>
            <strong>继续</strong>
            <p>商品事实已确认，当前图片也有真实角度依据。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="gate-case wait">
            <span>缺事实</span>
            <strong>标记待补</strong>
            <p>例如尺寸、重量、包装清单。不能猜，但不一定阻塞所有图片。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="gate-case stop">
            <span>缺角度</span>
            <strong>暂停这张图</strong>
            <p>明确告诉用户缺什么照片，并给出补拍要求。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="shoot-request">
          <div class="shoot-copy">
            <span>真实分支示例</span>
            <strong>要做 Type-C 接口图，但没有接口实拍</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="shoot-route">
            <span>不能让 AI 猜接口位置</span>
            <i>→</i>
            <span>暂停该图片任务</span>
            <i>→</i>
            <strong>让用户补拍接口近景</strong>
          </div>
          <small>建议说明：拍清接口完整位置、机身侧面结构、光线清楚、不要遮挡。</small>
        </div>
      </div>

      <span class="flow-arrow">↓</span>

      <div class="state-layer" aria-label="两个核心状态文件">
        <article class="state-file plan-file">
          <span class="file-role">整套方案状态</span>
          <strong>商品图片生成计划.md</strong>
          <p>保存商品事实、竞品结论、评价结论、卖点分级、主图规划、详情图规划、禁止项和待补资料。</p>
          <small>整套方向错了，先查这里。</small>
        </article>

        <span class="state-arrow">→</span>

        <div class="human-confirm">
          <span>HUMAN CHECKPOINT</span>
          <strong>运营确认</strong>
          <p>确认首图方向、最大卖点、文案和禁止内容。</p>
        </div>

        <span class="state-arrow">→</span>

        <article class="state-file task-file">
          <span class="file-role">单张执行状态</span>
          <strong>商品图片单图任务.md</strong>
          <p>保存某一张图的目标、文案、参考图片、允许修改、禁止修改和审核标准。</p>
          <small>只有某张图有问题，先查这里。</small>
        </article>
      </div>

      <span class="flow-arrow">↓</span>

      <div class="generation-layer">
        <div class="reference-box">
          <span>真实产品图</span>
          <strong>角度依据 + 结构依据</strong>
        </div>
        <span>+</span>
        <div class="reference-box">
          <span>单图任务</span>
          <strong>目标 + 文案 + 禁止项</strong>
        </div>
        <span>→</span>
        <div class="generator-box">
          <span>IMAGE MODEL</span>
          <strong>GPT Image 2</strong>
          <small>负责执行画面，不负责重新定义商品</small>
        </div>
        <span>→</span>
        <div class="review-box">
          <span>人工审核</span>
          <strong>通过 / 返回修改</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="layer-index" aria-label="项目排查层级">
    <div class="section-heading compact">
      <span class="eyebrow">WHERE TO LOOK</span>
      <h3>以后排查项目，可以先按这 6 层找</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="layer-list">
      <div><span>L1</span><strong>入口层</strong><small>ecommerce-product-image</small></div>
      <div><span>L2</span><strong>专业分析层</strong><small>competitor-analysis / review-analysis</small></div>
      <div><span>L3</span><strong>资料闸门</strong><small>商品事实 / 实拍角度 / 图片质量</small></div>
      <div><span>L4</span><strong>整套计划层</strong><small>商品图片生成计划.md</small></div>
      <div><span>L5</span><strong>单图执行层</strong><small>商品图片单图任务.md</small></div>
      <div><span>L6</span><strong>生成与审核层</strong><small>真实参考图 / GPT Image 2 / 人工审核</small></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</section>

